  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  header: 'Secure and Lift the Crankshaft:'
  body: "\u2022Carefully attach the crane hook to the crankshaft, double-checking
    that the connections are secure.\n\n\u2022Slowly lift the crankshaft, ensuring
    it remains level and stable as it rises, then move it towards the highlighted
    placement area."
