  header: 'Insert Each Piston Carefully:'
  body: "\u2022Select each piston individually, inspecting for defects, and apply
    a thin layer of lubricant if required.\n\n\u2022Gently guide each piston into
    the chassis, ensuring they align with the designated markings and slide smoothly."
