  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  header: 'Secure the Bearing Cap with Screwdriver:'
  body: "\u2022Using a screwdriver, tighten each bolt on the bearing cap incrementally,
    going in a cross-pattern to distribute pressure evenly.\n\n\u2022Perform a final
    check on each bolt to ensure it is secure and does not over-tighten, which could
    damage the bearing cap.\n"
  NextButtonText: Next
  PrevButtonText: Prev
  IsNext: 1
  IsPrev: 1
--- !u!114 &6071193582940631670
